column2: SELECT TOP #   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.extinction_i   ISNULL(s.specobjid,#) AS specobjid, ISNULL(s.z, #) AS zs ,ISNULL(s.class, #) AS class , ISNULL(s.subclass, #) AS subclass   wi.w1mag AS w1 and wi.w2mag AS w2    FROM PhotoObj AS p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN WISE_allsky AS wi ON wi.coadd_id = p.objid
